"**I 'm the One Mama Warned You About**" is a song written by Mickey James and
[Gayle Zeiler](/wiki/Kacey_Jones "Kacey Jones"), and recorded by American
country music artist [Mickey Gilley](/wiki/Mickey_Gilley "Mickey Gilley"). It
was released in January 1985 as the second and final single from his album
_[Too Good to Stop Now](/wiki/Too_Good_to_Stop_Now_\(album\) "Too Good to Stop
Now \(album\)")_. The song reached number 10 on the U.S.
_[Billboard](/wiki/Billboard_\(magazine\) "Billboard \(magazine\)")_ [Hot
Country Singles](/wiki/Hot_Country_Songs "Hot Country Songs") chart[1] and
number 10 on the Canadian _[RPM](/wiki/RPM_\(magazine\) "RPM \(magazine\)")_
Country Tracks chart in Canada.
